pii-zh-qwen 0.2.0rc1 community candidate
Copyright 2026 pii-zh-qwen contributors

This local research release candidate contains a Simplified-Chinese PII token-classification
model, its reproducibility tooling, and a Presidio/rules/model community cascade integration.

Model initialization is bound to `ZJUICSR/AIguard-pii-detection-fast` at revision
`677a5ebc1600fef61e8973cafd3026be322b3a73`. The upstream model card declares Apache-2.0;
upstream attribution and license terms apply independently to those materials.

Exact third-party revisions, roles, distribution boundaries, and dependency records for this
candidate are documented in THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md, the typed SBOM/license artifacts, and
`uv.lock`. Final human/legal license approval remains a separate publication gate.
